<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>757</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>nǐ shì wǒ de zhǔ 迦南757</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì wǒ de zhǔ, nǐ shì zào wǒ de zhǔ.
 wǒ lái dào nǐ miàn qián, xiàng nǐ fǔ fú.
 shēn shēn de jìng bài, cóng nèi xīn fā chū.
 yīn wèi zhǔ gěi wǒ de ēn diǎn, shù dōu shù bù qīng chǔ.
 wǒ yuàn yì jiàng fú, wǒ yuàn yì shùn fú.
 màn màn de lù tú shàng, wǒ bù huì gū dú.
 nǐ shì wǒ de zhǔ, nǐ shì zào wǒ de zhǔ.
 wǒ yuàn yì shēn shēn de shùn fú. shēn shēn de shùn fú.</lyrics>
</song>